    narr:generatedFrom "3c991f09974363b4cce27a05562b1dbbb93cb725" ;
    narr:narration """Aswritten’s narrative spine has evolved from a focus on [organizational memory](narr:Narrative_OrgMemoryDemotedToGovernanceSub) toward a more precise [steering-loop-plus-substrate](narr:Narrative_SteeringLoopPlusMemorySubstrate) model. The core [value proposition](narr:Position_CoreValuePropInstallExpertise) has shifted from general intelligence to [installable expertise](narr:Obs_ScarletInstallableExpertise), framing the product as a [velocity vector](narr:Narrative_NarrativeAsVector) that fills the [white space](narr:Narrative_WhiteSpaceMechanism) of LLM defaults with specific organizational perspective. 

This trajectory is anchored by the [AI-as-new-hire](narr:Narrative_AIAsNewHireBridgingInsight) metaphor, which bridges the gap between [solo-professional](narr:Obs_PitchDirectionSolo) and [agent-deployment](narr:Position_PitchReframeAgentDeployment) use cases. The product identity is increasingly defined by [Synthesized Individual Intelligence (SII)](narr:Narrative_SII_SynthesizedIndividualIntelligence), a portable, owned alternative to lab-centric AGI. Founder Scarlet Dame’s own [queer and trans identity](narr:Narrative_QueerRepresentationGrounding) provides the personal grounding for an [anti-monoculture thesis](narr:Narrative_QueerRepresentationGrounding), positioning the platform as a tool for truthful representation rather than generic diversity. The [business plan](narr:Narrative_BusinessPlanAsSource) now serves as the internal source of truth, while the [founder’s personal vision](narr:Narrative_FounderAsAuthorityLayer) acts as a distinct, cyclical credibility layer.""" ;
